data.description: Freshly Updated Rancher! Everything you need is on one level. This home has NEW stainless steel appliances, NEW windows/slider door, NEW breaker panel, NEW wood/laminate flooring, FRESH interior paint, NEW tiled bath/shower and more! Plus, the backyard is spacious and fully fenced! As an added bonus, the garage has been converted to a large bonus space. Quiet neighborhood close to military installations and every amenity imaginable! Come take a look, we think you'll love it! Be sure to take the 3D Tour for a better feel of the floor-plan!
